Srce. Ja sam Moana...

00:32:24.268 --> 00:32:26.652
od Matu...

00:32:28.255 --> 00:32:30.255
Nuija..."

00:32:41.294 --> 00:32:43.294
Hei-Hei?

00:33:04.671 --> 00:33:09.045
U redu je. Dobro si. Vidiš?

